{"data":[{"name":"84:1","price":"1਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਅਕਾਸ਼ ਫੱਟ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5885,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:2","price":"2਼ ਅਤੇ ਉਹ ਆਪਣੇ ਰੱਬ ਦੇ ਹੁਕਮਾਂ ਦੀ ਪਾਲਣਾ ਕਰੇਗਾ ਅਤੇ ਇਹੋ ਉਸ ਲਈ ਹੱਕ ਬਣਦਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5886,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:3","price":"3਼ ਜਦੋਂ ਧਰਤੀ ਫੈਲਾਈ ਜਾਵੇਗੀ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5887,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:4","price":"4਼ ਅਤੇ ਉਸ ਦੇ ਅੰਦਰ ਜੋ ਵੀ ਹੈ ਉਹ ਉਸ ਨੂੰ ਬਾਹਰ ਸੁੱਟ ਦੇਵੇਗੀ ਅਤੇ ਖਾਲੀ ਹੋ ਜਾਵੇਗੀ।","arabic":"وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5888,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:5","price":"5਼ ਅਤੇ (ਇੰਜ) ਉਹ ਆਪਣੇ ਰੱਬ ਦੇ ਹੁਕਮਾਂ ਦੀ ਪਾਲਣਾ ਕਰੇਗੀ ਅਤੇ ਉਸ ਦਾ ਹੱਕ ਵੀ ਇਹੋ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5889,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:6","price":"6਼ (ਹੇ ਮਨੁੱਖ! ਤੂੰ ਆਪਣੇ ਰੱਬ ਵੱਲ (ਜਾਣ ਲਈ) ਕਰੜੀ ਮਿਹਨਤ ਕਰ ਰਿਹਾ ਹੈ, ਅੰਤ ਤੂੰ ਉਸ ਨੂੰ ਮਿਲਣ ਵਾਲਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5890,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:7","price":"7਼ ਬਸ ਜਿਸ ਦੀ ਕਰਮ-ਪੱਤਰੀ ਉਸ ਦੇ ਸੱਜੇ ਹੱਥ ਵਿਚ ਦਿੱਤੀ ਜਾਵੇਗੀ।","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5891,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:8","price":"8਼ ਤਾਂ ਛੇਤੀ ਹੀ ਉਸ ਤੋਂ ਸੌਖਾ ਹਿਸਾਬ ਲਿਆ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5892,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:9","price":"9਼ ਉਹ ਆਪਣੇ ਆਪਣੇ ਜਹਿ (ਨੇਕ ਲੋਕਾਂ) ਵੱਲ ਖ਼ੁਸ਼ੀ ਖ਼ੁਸ਼ੀ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5893,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:10","price":"10਼ ਅਤੇ ਜਿਸ ਦੀ ਕਰਮ-ਪੱਤਰੀ ਉਸ ਦੀ ਪਿੱਠ ਪਿੱਛਿਓ ਫੜਾਈ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5894,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:11","price":"11਼ ਤਾਂ ਉਹ ਜ਼ਰੂਰ ਹੀ ਬਰਬਾਦੀ ਨੂੰ ਸੱਦੇਗਾ।","arabic":"فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5895,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:12","price":"12਼ ਅਤੇ ਉਹ ਭੜਕਦੀ ਹੋਈ ਅਗੱ ਵਿਚ ਸੁੱਟਿਆ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5896,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:13","price":"13਼ ਬੇਸ਼ੱਕ ਉਹ (ਸੰਸਾਰ ਵਿਚ) ਆਪਣੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ (ਆਪਣੇ ਜਿਿਹਆਂ) ਵਿਚ ਬਹੁਤ ਖ਼ੁਸ਼ ਸੀ।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5897,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:14","price":"14਼ ਬੇਸ਼ੱਕ ਉਹ ਸਮਝਦਾ ਸੀ ਕਿ ਉਹ ਕਦੇ ਵੀ (ਅੱਲਾਹ ਵੱਲ) ਮੁੜਕੇ ਨਹੀਂ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ।","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5898,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:15","price":"15਼ ਕਿਉਂ ਨਹੀਂ (ਜਾਵੇਗਾ), ਉਸ ਦਾ ਰੱਬ ਉਸ ਨੂੰ ਵੇਖ ਰਿਹਾ ਸੀ।","arabic":"بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5899,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:16","price":"16਼ ਸੋ ਮੈਂ ਸਹੁੰ ਖਾਂਦਾ ਹਾਂ ਸੰਝ ਵੇਲੇ ਦੀ ਲਾਲੀ ਦੀ।","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5900,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:17","price":"17਼ ਅਤੇ ਰਾਤ ਦੀ ਅਤੇ ਉਸ ਦੀ ਜੋ ਕੁੱਝ ਉਹ ਸਮੇਟ ਲੈਂਦੀ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5901,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:18","price":"18਼ ਅਤੇ ਚੰਨ ਦੀ ਜਦੋਂ ਉਹ ਪੂਰਾ ਹੁੰਦਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5902,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:19","price":"19਼ ਤੁਸੀਂ (ਲੋਕ) ਜ਼ਰੂਰ ਹੀ ਇਕ ਹਾਲਤ ਤੋਂ ਦੂਜੀ ਹਾਲਤ ਵੱਲ ਦਰਜਾ-ਬ-ਦਰਜਾ ਪਹੁੰਚ ਰਹੇ ਹੋ।","arabic":"لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5903,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:20","price":"20਼ ਫੇਰ ਇਹਨਾਂ (ਇਨਕਾਰੀਆਂ) ਨੂੰ ਕੀ ਹੋ ਗਿਆ ਕਿ ਉਹ ਈਮਾਨ ਨਹੀਂ ਲਿਆਏ ?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5904,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:21","price":"21਼ ਅਤੇ ਜਦੋਂ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਅੱਗੇ .ਕੁਰਆਨ ਪੜ੍ਹਿਆ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਤਾਂ ਉਹ ਸਿਜਦਾ ਨਹੀਂ ਕਰਦੇ।","arabic":"وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5905,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:22","price":"22਼ ਸਗੋਂ ਕਾਫ਼ਿਰ ਤਾਂ (.ਕੁਰਆਨ ਨੂੰ) ਝੁਠਲਾਉਂਦੇ ਹਨ।1","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5906,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1 ਵੇਖੋ ਸੂਰਤ ਆਲੇ-ਇਮਰਾਨ, ਹਾਸ਼ੀਆ ਆਇਤ 85/3","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:23","price":"23਼ ਅਤੇ ਜੋ ਕੁੱਝ ਵੀ ਉਹ (ਆਪਣੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਵਿਚ) ਸੁਰੱਖਿਅਤ ਰੱਖਦੇ ਹਨ ਅੱਲਾਹ ਉਹਨਾਂ (ਗੱਲਾਂ) ਨੂੰ ਭਲੀ-ਭਾਂਤ ਜਾਣਦਾ ਹੈ।","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5907,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:24","price":"24਼ ਤੁਸੀਂ (ਹੇ ਮੁਹੰਮਦ ਸ:!) ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਦੁਖਦਾਈ ਅਜ਼ਾਬ ਦੀ ਖ਼ੁਸ਼ਖ਼ਬਰੀ ਸੁਣਾ ਦਿਓ।","arabic":"فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5908,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"},{"name":"84:25","price":"25਼ ਪਰ ਜਿਹੜੇ ਲੋਕ ਅੱਲਾਹ ਅਤੇ ਰਸੂਲ ਉੱਤੇ ਈਮਾਨ ਲਿਆਏ ਅਤੇ ਉਹਨਾਂ ਨੇ ਨੇਕ ਕਰਮ ਵੀ ਕੀਤੇ, ਉਹਨਾਂ ਲਈ ਨਾ ਮੁੱਕਣ ਵਾਲਾ ਅਜਰ (ਬਦਲਾ) ਹੈ।","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ","category":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq"],"ayahNumber":5909,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"pa"}],"chapter":["84 (Al-Inshiqaq)","Al-Inshiqaq","Surah Al-Inshiqaq","Chapter Al-Inshiqaq","Inshiqaq","Surah Inshiqaq","Chapter Inshiqaq","Al Inshiqaq","Surah Al Inshiqaq","Chapter Al Inshiqaq","Surah 84","Chapter 84","The Splitting Open","الإنشقاق"]}